description: >-
  Express backend patterns for TaskFlow routes, services, and middleware. Enforces
  ApiResponse<T> wrappers, AppError with next(err) error handling, validate middleware
  on all POST/PATCH routes, async service functions that return unwrapped data, and
  naming conventions (kebab-case routes, camelCase services, PascalCase DTOs).
globs: src/{routes,services,middleware}/**/*
alwaysApply: true
